1
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,439
Xiao Bai

2
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,159
There is something

3
00:01:43,959 --> 00:01:45,040
I've always wanted to ask you.

4
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:50,719
You...

5
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:52,879
...are you...

6
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,040
I am not.

7
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,079
I haven't finished speaking.

8
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,000
I know what you want to say.

9
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,200
I am not.

10
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:03,719
Xiao Bai.

11
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:06,920
Tell me,

12
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,199
would Zhao Yun kill someone?

13
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:14,240
Assassin!

14
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:16,120
After him, quick!

15
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:16,599
Keep quiet.

16
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:17,879
Search the place!

17
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,159
Where is he?

18
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,280
Hurry up!

19
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:22,520
Young Master Ye.

20
00:02:23,599 --> 00:02:24,479
Reinforcements from Dali Temple have arrived.

21
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:25,759
I'll take you to Master Kun.

22
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,360
Where is Master Kun?

23
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:27,680
He is protecting a young lady.

24
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:30,639
What time is it now?

25
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:31,520
It is the Hour of the Dog.

26
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:32,159
Let's go.

27
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,240
Go.

28
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:40,960
Come and take a look!

29
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:50,759
The world bows to the Nine Thousand Years,

30
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,520
selling titles and offices, serving whom?

31
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:56,439
Trampling lives, levying heavy taxes,

32
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:59,280
sending defense maps to the border,

33
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:02,879
faking decrees to borrow imperial might,

34
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,919
harming colleagues, setting private rules,

35
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,800
wickedness overflowing, three thousand crimes,

36
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,319
Baixiao Villa takes a share.

37
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:11,759
Look.

38
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,879
Where did this come from?

39
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,360
Go back to your room and stay there.

40
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,000
Do not come out, no matter what.

41
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,719
I'll go with you.

42
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,680
No, don't drag me down.

43
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:27,080
Then I'll kill myself.

44
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,439
I won't drag you down.

45
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,479
Fine.

46
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,599
Then stay close to me.

47
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,159
Let's go.

48
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:39,000
Go.

49
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:49,840
Ye Li!

50
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,599
Young Master Ye, fortunately we had your help.

51
00:03:59,240 --> 00:03:59,879
How are you?

52
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,479
I'm fine.

53
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:03,280
Let's capture Eunuch Liu first.

54
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:04,879
Otherwise, there will be no proof.

55
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:05,719
Okay, let's go.

56
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:11,000
Careful.

57
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,240
Careful, it might be a trap.

58
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:29,000
Eunuch Liu.

59
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:31,519
Why are you drinking tea here alone?

60
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,480
You were making such a racket outside,

61
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,839
I found it annoying.

62
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:38,920
Let me ask you,

63
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,959
you came to Baixiao Villa

64
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,639
just to locate the Thousand Mechanism Secret Treasure,

65
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:45,040
then destroy it

66
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:46,519
and frame the Crown Prince.

67
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:48,480
Is that true or not?

68
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:53,879
Young Master Ye,

69
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:56,519
I am merely acting on orders.

70
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:24,120
I have already sent a signal.

71
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:25,959
The Dark Investigation Division

72
00:05:26,079 --> 00:05:27,759
will arrive in two hours.

73
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,199
None of you

74
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,360
will be able to escape.

75
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:37,600
Let's go.

76
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:39,519
If we don't leave now, once they arrive,

77
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,439
it will be hard to get away.

78
00:05:41,399 --> 00:05:41,839
Master Kun.

79
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:43,319
Time is tight.

80
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,000
Please catch the murderer as soon as possible.

81
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,600
You...

82
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,240
Master Kun,

83
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:48,079
we are under orders

84
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:50,079
to supervise you and Litigator Ye in the investigation.

85
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:51,439
Once the true culprit is caught,

86
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,519
we will escort you safely away.

87
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:55,519
Aren't you on the same side?

88
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:57,680
Wearing our uniforms,

89
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,680
but they are men from the Palace.

90
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:04,720
Ye Li!

91
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,160
Young Master Ye!

92
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:05,879
Ye Li!

93
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,319
Young Master Ye!

94
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,720
Ye Li!

95
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,160
Ye Li!

96
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,319
He's dead.

97
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,720
Ye Li

98
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:45,639
Ye Li

99
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,800
The Secret Investigation Division is on the way.

100
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,879
We don't have much time left.

101
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,000
I can tell you the truth.

102
00:06:58,639 --> 00:06:59,680
But you must promise me.

103
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:02,279
Everyone in the villa today...

104
00:07:02,279 --> 00:07:03,439
...will not die here.

105
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,759
I will do my best.

106
00:07:22,319 --> 00:07:23,759
I told Eunuch Liu before...

107
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,879
...that eating the Jing flowers in the courtyard with fish...

108
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,319
...can produce a deadly poison.

109
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:29,800
That is true.

110
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:31,839
Therefore,

111
00:07:34,839 --> 00:07:36,680
whoever has the scent of Jing flowers on them...

112
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:39,360
...is the most suspicious.

113
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:42,879
The day I first arrived at the villa,

114
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,839
as soon as I entered the main hall,

115
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,600
I noticed that scent.

116
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,000
On the day Huang Cui died,

117
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,439
around her body...

118
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,920
...I also smelled the scent of Jing flowers.

119
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:12,399
Siniang,

120
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,759
I suspect you got pollen on your fingertips...

121
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:17,879
...and fed the fish cake to Huang Cui...

122
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,680
...right under Eunuch Liu's nose...

123
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:22,319
...to poison her.

124
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:24,079
Eunuch.

125
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,079
I prepared some for her too.

126
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:29,920
Should I give it to her?

127
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,000
Feed her a little.

128
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,600
Otherwise, if she starves to death,

129
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:36,159
we won't be able to get any answers.

130
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:54,919
Eat something.

131
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:15,000
I thought you did it to avenge the Villa Master...

132
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:17,799
...and that's why you killed Huang Cui.

133
00:09:18,519 --> 00:09:20,000
I once firmly believed that answer.

134
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,279
But that day,

135
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:24,440
when I led Xiao Bai into the cave,

136
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:27,120
on the hairpin atop her head...

137
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,639
...I smelled the same scent.

138
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,639
Don't be afraid.

139
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,039
So there is more than one murderer.

140
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:41,159
Pollen is not easy to carry.

141
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:42,879
Putting it in a pouch...

142
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:44,879
...would arouse suspicion.

143
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,679
I guess you put the pollen...

144
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,919
...in the grooves of the hairpin...

145
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,320
...and passed it using the hairpin.

146
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,720
If that is so,

147
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,240
then tell me,

148
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:23,240
why did she want to kill Huang Cui?
